snippet.title: Gutsy the Guinea Pig: Reveal Trailer - Drizzle Games
snippet.description:
Gutsy the Guinea Pig is our premiere game as Drizzle Games, a two man indie dev team comprised of Omni Jacala and Phil Ogden. Gutsy is a physics puzzle game based on magnetism, with a bite-sized spin on speedrunning.

The game will be launching on iOS and Android later this year.

Join our discord server to stay up to date and even apply to be a playtester:
https://discord.gg/XRTD5nV

#GutsyGame #GutsyGuineaPig #Gutsy
